{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh reigns! Let the peoples tremble. He sits enthroned among the cherubim."
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Let the earth be moved."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh is great in Zion. He is high above all the peoples."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Let them praise your great and awesome name. He is Holy!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "The King’s strength also loves justice. You establish equity."
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "You execute justice and righteousness in Jacob."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Exalt Yahweh our God. Worship at his footstool."
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "He is Holy!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Moses and Aaron were among his priests, Samuel was among those who call on his name."
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "They called on Yahweh, and he answered them."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "He spoke to them in the pillar of cloud. They kept his testimonies,"
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "the statute that he gave them."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "You answered them, Yahweh our God. You are a God who forgave them,"
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "although you took vengeance for their doings."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "9",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Exalt Yahweh, our God. Worship at his holy hill,"
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "for Yahweh, our God, is holy!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}